OL,3,CNottingham City Council leader to
OL,4,Cleave role
OL,6,FDavid Mellen has announced he will not
OL,7,Fstand again to be Nottingham City
OL,8,FCouncil's leader.
OL,10,FEvery year, the Labour Group
OL,11,Fcontrolling Nottingham council meets
OL,12,Fto decide who its leadership team will
OL,13,Fbe for the next 12 months.
OL,15,FIt is understood that Councillor
OL,16,FMellen told his 49 fellow Labour
OL,17,Fcouncillors at an online meeting on
OL,18,FMonday night (March 11) that he will
OL,19,Fnot be putting his name forward to be
OL,20,Fthe leader again when that annual
OL,21,Fmeeting comes around.
