OL,3,CNottingham City Council leader to
OL,4,Cleave role
OL,6,FThe council issued a section 114
OL,7,Fnotice in November and government
OL,8,Fappointed commissioners were brought
OL,9,Fin to help run the authority in
OL,10,FFebruary.
OL,12,FThe council had been struggling with
OL,13,Fit's finances since the collapse of
OL,14,Fcouncil firm Robin Hood Energy in
OL,15,F2020, which cost the taxpayer an
OL,16,Festimated #38million.
OL,18,FThe Government had previously said it
OL,19,Fwas 'minded' to out of the Housing
OL,20,FRevenue Account.
